import React from 'react'
import './App.css'
import ComboBanner from './components/ComboBanner'
import Header from './components/Header'
import Menu from './components/Menu'

function App() {
  return (
    <main>
      <Header />
      <ComboBanner />
      <Menu />
    </main>
  )
}

export default App
